{"tid":2007664,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)妖夜尋狼1-4","createTime":"2020-05-08T12:39:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T21:23:51.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"06d9ed8edee072e0000618c2f3be8c6720a8a134","tid":2007664,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T12:39:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQOSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=2e92573b\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQOSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=b8ad1aa2\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQOSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=d596013f\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/bluelqe/1331112151-1328898984.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fbluelqe%2F1331112151-1328898984.jpg&h=30200af1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.時為現代歐洲城市夜空，正當人類熟睡時，吸血鬼與人狼之血戰才揭開序幕。數千年來，萊根族人狼本是吸血鬼貴族日間的守護獸，卻在15世紀前，一次奴隸階級的大革命，埋藏在吸血鬼族百年典故的恩仇錄，成為兩族鬥爭的楔子。經過數百年黑暗之戰，兩族鬼神亦隨時代變遷，研製出各種針對敵人弱點高科技武器；日光子彈、水銀導彈，雷霆飛鏢，神鋼寶劍等等層出不窮，雙方在夜幕下展開血腥，滅絕大屠殺的背後，卻牽涉一段至死不渝的情史..<br />\n<br />\n2.承接上集，吸血鬼族死亡使者施蓮殺死了吸血鬼長老域陀，成了族中的頭號獵物；而被她咬到的人狼麥可變成了人狼和吸血鬼的混種後，擁有無人所知的力量。續集以二人的逃亡為序幕，他們要前往尋找另一位吸血鬼長老馬卡斯，希望向他解釋他們的苦衷。可惜長老未被其所動，誓要將二人置之死地..<br />\n<br />\n3.在異世界決戰開打前一千多年，兩個超自然生物種族誕生了，他們分屬不死的亞歷山大柯維尼的兩支後裔。出身自馬可士一族的吸血鬼，優雅、高尚，是狡猾的飲血生物；而來自威廉一族的狼族，則成為野蠻的怪獸，毫無人性，嗜血暴力。吸血鬼靠著他們高人一等的智慧、力量與政治技巧，統治了現今的匈牙利西部荒地一帶，但他們仍懼怕狼族，儘管後者缺乏組織力與深刻思考能力，他們的力量卻是無比強大、兇殘<br />\n<br />\n4.劇情描述狼族與吸血鬼的戰爭千年未了，吸血鬼戰士莎倫娜〈凱特貝琴薩 飾〉卻落入人類之手，囚禁成為實驗品長達12年之久。當莎倫娜醒來脫逃後，卻發現在高科技的未來世界裡，狼族與吸血鬼不只勢力不在，還淪為人類撲殺的獵物。正當狼族與吸血鬼陷入慌亂求生之際，莎倫娜還發現，有一個更具毀滅性的神祕生物進逼威脅，讓這場人、狼、吸血鬼三角大戰更撲朔迷離&hellip;&hellip;。<br />\n<br />\n8 50PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔一定播5<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQOSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=cb431a37\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQOSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=7d7a608a\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f61facab6189d8838ac63be4bf80674d3a3d1658","tid":2007664,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T12:41:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clo